<Story><p aid:pstyle="NoIndent">Sometimes the players will come across someone who becomes important in the moment. When the ritual goes wrong and a poor captive gets the power cosmic, what does that villager do with it? Who were they?</p>
<p>When you need a quick NPC, all you need is an instinct and some way to pursue it. We call that a Knack, it can be anything from a skill to a title to a debt owed. Combine the two, and you have an NPC who has something they want and a way to try to get it, and you're ready to go.</p>
